{"tid":1618914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[大審批日] 人無人覺得香港即將淪陷好興奮？","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:50:07.000Z","uid":243928,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a53c67416124818bf3a6c1ec1f87a641785a3fab","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"引用緊急法，蒙面法已經唔重要。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭可以直接抄李嘉誠家。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭可以要求18歲處女服侍黑警。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭可以重新通過送中條例。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好興奮。<br />\n<br />\n真正的攬炒即將來臨。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀，津巴布韋黑歷史、委內瑞拉內戰。<br />\n<br />\n以上都係獨裁政府的結果，醫生律師工程師都要做雞去養家，男殺女姦，一語成讖。"},{"pid":"b9be2de248bb5f9194dd1fe66e3c0e8d91ec93af","tid":1618914,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"超興奮呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504a65c2bdb5af9156326c5784dacd382cc4b5b3","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"來吧"},{"pid":"6f53c024d870396707488321d1f887cc746b1821","tid":1618914,"uid":276319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec43456c712588825c6f83f0099cbe5f337fb37","tid":1618914,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"樓主興奮到字都打錯"},{"pid":"50424cb0892e5e89e6177055707cc7a8c746e6eb","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"津巴布韋本身是一個礦產資源豐富，土地肥沃的國家，曾經的經濟實力僅次於南非。1980年津巴布韋獨立，政府同時發行了第一代津巴布韋元，貨幣代碼是ZWD。最開始津巴布韋元甚至比美元還值錢，當時津巴布韋元與美元匯率為1:1.47。當然，這並不是津巴布韋元的真實價值，隨着時間流逝，津巴布韋元不斷貶值。<br />\n隨着2000年總統穆加貝推行激進的土地改革，強行沒收白人農場主的土地，津巴布韋經濟一蹶不振，津巴布韋元也開始了急劇貶值之路。到2006年時，在黑市上一百萬津巴布韋元才能兌換1英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/3jljn53.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2F3jljn53.html&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=25b2c720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/3jljn53.html</a>"},{"pid":"cfd4a90c547913b1b9b15a07674d387b57fd9674","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"一個國家，兩個總統 委內瑞拉又怎麼了？<br />\n國際貨幣基金預測，委內瑞拉通貨膨脹率恐怕2019年達1000萬%，超過300萬人活不下去，不得不出逃。現在，這個國家竟然出現了兩個總統，委內瑞拉究竟發生什麼事？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/project/cards/20190124-venezuela/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fproject%2Fcards%2F20190124-venezuela%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=82d19fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/project/cards/20190124-venezuela/</a>"},{"pid":"5d51d7fa4436e7d2bf7f9148dc4c7622057cfb29","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"202e86f587ba8e7ad865ebaa38fc7453b894b168","tid":1618914,"uid":285117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec43456c712588825c6f83f0099cbe5f337fb37","tid":1618914,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"樓主興奮到字都打錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7800d8347107c5484715253ee93d0cbce12debf8","tid":1618914,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"41974d009e3b9d8cf3d041b6f32ce3e9822e0cbf","tid":1618914